sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User
  participant Browser as WarGamingModeClient
  participant Hook as useWarGamingBootstrap
  participant API as GET /api/war-gaming/bootstrap
  participant Shared as withDb/readSettings
  participant DB as SQLite

  User->>Browser: Open war-gaming route
  Browser->>Hook: initial refresh()
  Hook->>API: GET bootstrap
  API->>Shared: withDb(fn)
  Shared->>DB: open/init database

  alt DB open or query fails
    DB-->>Shared: exception
    Shared-->>API: throw error
    API-->>Hook: 500 {error,traceId,debug}
    Hook-->>Browser: error state set
    Browser-->>User: "Loading War Gaming..." replaced with error text
  else DB healthy
    DB-->>Shared: projection rows
    Shared-->>API: payload
    API-->>Hook: 200 payload
    Hook-->>Browser: data state set
  end
